    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no smells, just pure perfection. You won't find another one this clean! Shoot me a message if you want to take a look!",
